PS. The NPS Unified Messages are based on ISO 20022 messages from the following functional areas:

– pain (Payment initiation);

– pacs (Payment clearing and settlements);

– camt (Cash management). The messages definitions of the NPS Unified Messages are presented in XLSХ \-files. Each of the NPS Unified Messages has its own name in accordance with the ISO 20022 standard.

